ginner 1 (0%)<br />Herbalist - Beginner 3 (2%)<br />Alchemy - Beginner 2 (0%)<br />Leatherworking - Beginner 2 (0%)<br />Blacksmithing - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Tailoring - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Enchanting - Beginner 2 (10%)<br />Architect - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Seduction - Basic 1 (0%)<br />Negotiation - Beginner 7 (0%)<br />Gambling - Beginner 5 (0%)<br />Disguise - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Lying - Beginner 6 (0%)<br />Sneak - Beginner 1 (10%)<br />Move Silently - Beginner 1 (10%)<br />Identify - Beginner 4 (18%)<br />Poisoner - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Observe - Beginner 6 (75%)<br />Sleight of Hand - Beginner 1 (0%)<br />Bow\xc2\xa0Mastery - Beginner 5 (0%)<br />Throwing - Beginner 2 (0%)<br />Intimidation - Beginner 3 (0%)<br />Whip Mastery - Beginner 5 (0%)<br />Training - Beginner 3 (0%)<br />Dagger Mastery - Beginner 5 (10%)<br />Hellfire Mastery - Beginner 1 (0%)</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Class Benefits</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>+20% with Dark Spells<br />+20 MP per Level<br />Light Armor Proficiency<br />Hellfire<br />Skills and Spells added<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Level 10: Hellfire Blade</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Sub-class Benefits</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Profession Benefits</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Slave Trainer<br />Gain skills, proficiencies, recipes.<br />+10% to Training<br />+15% to Whips<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Level 10: Obedience Training \xe2\x80\x93 Slaves under your command are more obedient, and better at following orders. Slaves are +5% to actions while following orders.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Perks</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Able Learner<br />Silver-Tongued Devil<br />Artisan Soul<br />Mercantile<br />Strength Focus<br />Dexterity Focus<br />Constitution Focus<br />Intelligence Focus<br />Wisdom Focus<br />Charisma Focus<br />Luck Focus<br />Soulforged Weapon (x2)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /></div></div></div><br /><br /