><td>None</td></tr><tr><td>HP</td><td>490/490</td><td>MP</td><td>200/200</td></tr><tr><td>HP Regen</td><td>2.0 per min</td><td>MP Regen</td><td>2.0 per min</td></tr><tr><td>Fame</td><td>0</td><td>Infamy</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>0 PP</td><td>1 GP</td><td>4 SP</td><td>160 CP</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Attributes</td></tr><tr><td>STR</td><td>35</td><td>INT</td><td>20</td></tr><tr><td>DEX</td><td>64</td><td>WIS</td><td>20</td></tr><tr><td>CON</td><td>35</td><td>CHA</td><td>25</td></tr><tr><td>Luck</td><td>15</td><td>Attack</td><td>+10</td></tr><tr><td>Defense</td><td>+15</td><td>???</td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Points Remaining: 0</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Titles</td><td colspan='3'>Slave</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Resistances</td></tr><tr><td>Pierce</td><td>+15%</td><td>Bludgeoning</td><td>+15%</td></tr><tr><td>Slash</td><td>+15%</td><td>Fire</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Ice</td><td></td><td>Water</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Lightning</td><td></td><td>Wind</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Earth</td><td></td><td>Light</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Dark</td><td></td><td>Charm</td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Enslaved to Zayn Darkmore \xe2\x80\x93 Compelled to follow all commands.<br />+15% dodge bonus<br />+15% crit rate</td></tr><tr><td>Diety</td><td colspan='3'>Necron</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Proficiencies</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Simple Weapons<br />Light Armor<br />Dual Wielding</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Skills</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Dagger Mastery - Beginner 8 (6%)<br />Sneak - Beginner 4 (10%)<br />Move Silently - Beginner 4 (10%)<br />Identify - Beginner 1 (18%)<br />Poisoner - Beginner 6 (0%)<br />Observe - Beginner 2 (75%)<br />Throwing - Beginner 5 (0%)<br />Dancing - Beginner 2 (0%)<br />Acrobatics - Beginner 2 (0%)</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Class Benefits</td></tr><tr><td c