    <div class="portlet-body">
                        <div class="chapter-inner chapter-content">
            Once we were out of the slave market, I made my way to a decent weapon\xe2\x80\x99s store. Yukiko had a beginner\xe2\x80\x99s sword and armor. While better than anything else my group had, that was still level 1 gear. Not going to cut it. Looking over my shoulder, I said to my new pet,<span style="color: #3366ff;"> \xe2\x80\x9cSo, Yukiko, what\xe2\x80\x99s your story? How\xe2\x80\x99d a Traveler end up a slave?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Yukiko\xe2\x80\x99s head fell, and she said, <span style="color: #ff3333;">\xe2\x80\x9cWell, I reincarnated my high level character from WOD here. I wasn\xe2\x80\x99t max level, but I was one of the high level blacksmiths in my guild, the Lords of Light. Unfortunately, I ran into some trouble with character creation. The abilities I got turned problematic.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cYes, I saw them on your status. Tell me what they mean. In detail, if you will.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Now she was blushing furiously. Oh, this had to be good!<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #ff3333;">\xe2\x80\x9cWell, \xe2\x80\x98Hurts so Good\xe2\x80\x99 converts all pain my character experiences into pleasure. I still take damage, but my avatar responds differently to it than others. \xe2\x80\x98Senpai Noticed Me!\xe2\x80\x99 gives me a +100% to any actions I take for 10 minutes after getting praised by someone important to me. \xe2\x80\x98Art of the Forge\xe2\x80\x99 gives me the Blacksmith profession, and Blacksmith at Basic 3, and I\xe2\x80\x99m able to repair gear without losing any durability. \xe2\x80\x98The Story of O\xe2\x80\x99, um, gave me this collar, and made me start as a slave. \xe2\x80\x98Lady Luck\xe2\x80\x99s Fool\xe2\x80\x99 sets my Luck to 0, and it can\xe2\x80\x99t ever be raised. \xe2\x80\x98Gullible\xe2\x80\x99s Travels\xe2\x80\x99 means that I\xe2\x80\x99m -30% to discern truth from lies.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I stood for a moment, stunned, and then laughed out loud. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cSo your browser history must be pretty interesting, Yukiko. So, why did you reincarnate to AAO?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #ff3333;">\xe2\x80\x9cUm, I had a crush on the guild leader, Torgan. He was the top Paladin in the game, you know! After we got the guild achievement for being the first to beat Frostcrown, he announced that he would be reincarnating here. I thought I could come too, and maybe get to know him better.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cSo you chased this Torgan to a new game. Did you tell him you were doing so? Or make any plans to meet?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #ff3333;">\xe2\x80\x9cUm, no. I was always shy around the guild leader.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cSo, what, you were just hoping to randomly find this person in the entire game world? And what if he went by a different name?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #ff3333;">\xe2\x80\x9cOh. I didn\xe2\x80\x99t think about that!\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cDon\xe2\x80\x99t worry, pet. I\xe2\x80\x99ll show you things you never dreamed of, even with that kinky browser history. Before I\xe2\x80\x99m done, you\xe2\x80\x99ll forget all about Torgan.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I was laughing to myself as we went about our shopping. To think that Kiyabu Yukiko, the former Warrior and max level blacksmith, would come chasing after me with some schoolgirl crush. She didn\xe2\x80\x99t even change her name! Anyways, I decided to get just a few basic items for Yukiko, since we could probably get better off drops. Also, I picked up a whip for myself. After enchanting everything, it looked like this:<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><div class='spoiler'><div class='smalltext' style='margin-bottom:2px'><b>Spoiler</b> : <input type='button' value='Show' class='spoilerButton'></div><div class='spoilerContent'><div style='display: none;'><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='4'>Tamer\xe2\x80\x99s Magic Whip</td></tr><tr><td>Type</td><td>Whip</td><td>Rank</td><td>Common</td></tr><tr><td>Damage</td><td>1 \xe2\x80\x93 5</td><td>Damage Type</td><td>Slashing</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>A standard leather whip, used by tamers of beasts and men for ages. While the damage is not great, the point is to provide pain as an encouragement for the target to behave. This whip has been enchanted to provide a slight healing benefit to those struck by it.<br />Durability: 15/15<br />\xc2\xa0<br />+20% Aggravation to opponent<br />15% chance of Disarming opponent<br />5% chance of tripping opponent<br />+5 Attack<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Enchanted:</span> Heals 1-10 points of damage to target on hit. Costs 1 MP</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><br /><br />And for Yukiko, I got:<br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='4'>Brilliant Bow</td></tr><tr><td>Type</td><td>Bow</td><td>Rank</td><td>Common</td></tr><tr><td>Damage</td><td>20 \xe2\x80\x93 30</td><td>Damage Type</td><td>Piercing</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>A common, though well made, longbow. This one has been enchanted with light magic, bestowing additional effects on the arrows fired from it.<br />Durability: 15/15<br />\xc2\xa0<br />+30 Attack<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Enchanted:</span> Deals 1-10 points of light damage to target on hit. x2 damage to Undead.</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='4'>Steel Frost Blade</td></tr><tr><td>Type</td><td>Sword (Katana)</td><td>Rank</td><td>Uncommon</td></tr><tr><td>Damage</td><td>10 \xe2\x80\x93 25</td><td>Damage Type</td><td>Slashing</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>A katana made from hardened steel. The craftsmanship is decent, though not the work of a master. A warrior\xe2\x80\x99s blade. This blade has been enchanted with ice magic.<br />Durability: 40/40<br />\xc2\xa0<br />+30 Attack<br />+10% to Parry blows<br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Enchanted:</span> Deals 1-10 Cold damage on contact.</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='4'>Hardened Lamellar Armor</td></tr><tr><td>Type</td><td>Armor</td><td>Rank</td><td>Common</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>This heavy armor is made from hardened leather plates, overlapping to provide defense equal to that of steel, with a fraction of the weight. This set has been made in the oroyoi style.<br />Durability: 200/200<br />Class Restriction: Samurai<br />\xc2\xa0<br />+50 Defense<br />+30% Resistance to Piercing, Slashing, and Bludgeoning<br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Enchanted:</span> +1 HP Regeneration/Minute</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /></div></div></div><br />\xc2\xa0<br />After finishing the day\xe2\x80\x99s shopping, I stopped by the guild hall again, so I could get my card. To my surprise, instructor Whitetail was by the counter when I came in, with my girls in tow.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cccc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cYou!\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cYes, me. I was told that my guild card would be ready by now.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cccc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cDamn Traveler! Look at yourself with your harem! Hey! Don\xe2\x80\x99t ignore me, damnit!\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I did ignore her, as I went to the counter. The clerk looked like he was trying desperately not to laugh, so I cut him a break, and spoke first. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAh, my name is Zayn Darkmore. I was to pick up my guild card today.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #99cc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cY-yes, of course.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> He pulled a card out from under the desk, and said, <span style="color: #99cc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cYou\xe2\x80\x99ll need a drop of blood to bind it to you, after which, it will automatically update your guild status whenever you complete quests or have other achievements of note.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> I pricked my finger, and dropped a bit of blood on the card.<span style="color: #99cc33;"> \xe2\x80\x9cExcellent. It appears that you\xe2\x80\x99ve been evaluated as a Rank E adventurer to start. Impressive for a newcomer. You must have done well in your tests.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cYes, I think I did well, especially in the magic one.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> I looked at the card to see what it said.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td>Name</td><td>Zayn Darkmore</td><td>Rank</td><td>E</td></tr><tr><td>Race</td><td>Incubus</td><td>Status</td><td>Traveler</td></tr><tr><td>Level</td><td>10</td><td>Class</td><td>Warlock</td></tr><tr><td>Profession</td><td>Slave Trainer</td><td>Subclass</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Titles</td><td colspan='3'>The Executioner, The Sexecutioner, Corrupter, Master Chainmaker</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br />\xc2\xa0<br />So, a condensed version of my status sheet, but this one could be shown to other people easily. And it didn\xe2\x80\x99t give away any really bad information. I\xe2\x80\x99m sure criminal guilds had fake versions available, if I wanted to go that route. Meanwhile, the clerk was still talking, while the instructor looked like she was about to explode due to my ignoring her.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #99cc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cThe guild card is accepted as proper identification in all lands; the Adventurer\xe2\x80\x99s Guild is not bound by national ties. You may store currency on your card, if you wish.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Ah, that\xe2\x80\x99s convenient. All those coins in my inventory were taking up space. When I put them on the card, I noticed something even more convenient. Instead of just tallying the number of coins on the card, they were converted to the smallest number possible. 14 GP, 32 SP, and 140 CP became 18 GP, 6 SP. When I asked the clerk about it, he simply said that it was part of the card\xe2\x80\x99s magic.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cccc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cHEY! STOP IGNORING ME, DAMNIT!\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I turned to look at the Instructor, and smiled.<span style="color: #3366ff;"> \xe2\x80\x9cOh, I\xe2\x80\x99m sorry, did you wish something, Instructor? I was going to entertain my new slave after dinner, but you\xe2\x80\x99re welcome to join in, if you like.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cccc33;">\xe2\x80\x9cYou bastard! Don\xe2\x80\x99t think just because\xe2\x80\x94\xe2\x80\x9c</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cYou know, we probably shouldn\xe2\x80\x99t cause a scene here, a lot of people are looking at you now, wondering why the Instructor is so interested in a new E-rank adventurer.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> I smiled wickedly at her. She froze, looked quickly at the attention we most definitely were attracting, and then turned and stormed off towards the stairs, muttering as she did so.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Looking back to the clerk, I said, <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cI\xe2\x80\x99m going to be heading to the Wyrmwood soon, do you know of any quests leading in that direction?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />The clerk, after he finished laughing, directed me to the quest board, and I picked out a few quests that would work.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><div class='spoiler'><div class='smalltext' style='margin-bottom:2px'><b>Spoiler</b> : <input type='button' value='Show' class='spoilerButton'></div><div class='spoilerContent'><div style='display: none;'><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='3'>New Quest: Bandit Subjugation<br />Bandits have been causing trouble along the Vermillion Road between Falon and Wyrmwood. Thin their numbers so that merchant wagons can get through!</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rank</td><td colspan='2'>D</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Success</td><td colspan='2'>Kill 20 Bandits</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Failure</td><td colspan='2'>Give up the Quest</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rewards</td><td colspan='2'>Experience<br />200 GP</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='3'>New Quest: Merchant Escort<br />Merchant Silas Horneby requests an escort for his wagon from Falon to Gepheart on the Vermillion Road.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rank</td><td colspan='2'>E</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Success</td><td colspan='2'>Silas Horneby and his cargo make it safely to Gepheart.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Failure</td><td colspan='2'>Silas Horneby dies or cargo lost</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rewards</td><td colspan='2'>50 GP<br />Unknown</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan='3'>New Quest: Becket\xe2\x80\x99s Furs<br />Hunter Becket has a load of 10 furs that needs to get to Gepheart on the Vermillion Road.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rank</td><td colspan='2'>F</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Success</td><td colspan='2'>Deliver 10 furs to the leatherworker in Gepheart.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Failure</td><td colspan='2'>Do not deliver the furs.</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Rewards</td><td colspan='2'>50 SP</td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Consequences</td><td colspan='2'>10 GP fine<br />Relationship with Falon decreases</td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /></div></div></div><br />\xc2\xa0<br />\xc2\xa0<br />(Later)<br />After dinner, my pets and I were once more in my room. Turning to look at Yukiko, I said, <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cNow, Yukiko. You told me earlier that you wanted to meet this \xe2\x80\x98Torgan\xe2\x80\x99 in game, yes? Well, I happen to know a few things about Torgan. If you endure everything I am about to do to you without logging out, then I will tell you something about Torgan that you will be only the second person in this world to know.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Oh, how her eyes lit up with both fear and excitement! I was going to thoroughly enjoy this. When she finally nodded her head, I smiled, and said, <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cNow, strip.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />&lt;Della POV&gt;<br />Master is so wicked! The Traveler he purchased at the market has no idea what she\xe2\x80\x99s in for, but she\xe2\x80\x99s going to go along with it blindly because she wants to know more about this \xe2\x80\x98Torgan\xe2\x80\x99. I can\xe2\x80\x99t wait to see her delicious pain when he takes her. Oh, wait, she said something about having an ability that turned pain to pleasure, right? Well, that takes some of the fun out of it.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />I wonder what he\xe2\x80\x99ll do to the girl? And what is this secret? Is it related to Master\xe2\x80\x99s incredible strength?<br />\xc2\xa0<br />&lt;Severa POV&gt;<br />Hah! Stupid bitch gets to take my place tonight! Bastard\xe2\x80\x99s going to rape her senseless. I just hope he forgets about my poor ass for a while. I didn\xe2\x80\x99t think they could get that big, even on an incubus! He must be part horse!<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Ugh, I still can\xe2\x80\x99t believe the bastard makes me call him \xe2\x80\x98Master\xe2\x80\x99 all the time. At least there are two other girls here who can take some of the attention away.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cSevera, Della, you two strip as well. Pleasure eachother while I entertain my new pet.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br /><br />DAMNIT! I\xe2\x80\x99m not even into girls! I hate how my body moves to take off my clothes at his command. I hate it even more that I know I\xe2\x80\x99m only allowed to wear those clothes because it makes me more effective in combat.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />No, don\xe2\x80\x99t touch me there you stupid slut! Oh, god, what is my tongue doing? What is her tongue doing? OHHHH!<br />\xc2\xa0<br />&lt;Yukiko POV&gt;<br />Oh. Oh fuck. Fuck fuck fuckity FUCK! I\xe2\x80\x99m going to get raped. That\xe2\x80\x99s what\xe2\x80\x99s going to happen, right? The two other slaves aren\xe2\x80\x99t much help. The blonde looks like she\xe2\x80\x99s about to cream herself in anticipation of whatever\xe2\x80\x99s going to happen. The black-haired one just gives me a look that says, \xe2\x80\x98better you than me\xe2\x80\x99. What has this bastard been doing to these girls?<br />\xc2\xa0<br />I gulp as I stand there, naked, presenting myself for him. I could log out. I could escape, and make a new character. But I would lose the bonuses from reincarnating if I did that. And I would lose my only chance to find out more about Torgan.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />The black-haired girl makes a look of distaste as Master (oh god, I\xe2\x80\x99m even thinking about him in those terms now!) tells the two other girls to go down on eachother for entertainment while he deals with me. As he passes behind me, I feel his hands pulling at my arms that were trying to shield my body, placing them behind my head. He moves my feet shoulder width apart, and then commands me not to move, locking my body in place.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />And then I see a sign of a new debuff come up on my HUD. \xe2\x80\x98Selfish Lover\xe2\x80\x99? And no duration? That means it will last until canceled? What the\xe2\x80\x94<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="font-style: italic;">CRACK!</span> The whip sings in the air before it cracks across my butt. I moan in pleasure, though I notice a red -2 and a green +3 come up. My HP bar hasn\xe2\x80\x99t changed at all. So I could literally be about to die of pain (well, pleasure for me) and I still wouldn\xe2\x80\x99t be able to die. Sick bastard.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Another crack, another moan. And again. And again, and oh GOD, it is so good! I can\xe2\x80\x99t take it! It feels like I\xe2\x80\x99m going to burst any moment now. But why can\xe2\x80\x99t I cum?<br />\xc2\xa0<br />After what seems like hours, but my HUD tells me is only twenty minutes, I\xe2\x80\x99m panting hard. I can\xe2\x80\x99t see straight from pleasure, but I still can\xe2\x80\x99t cum! And then I see that, sometime while he\xe2\x80\x99s been playing with me, he managed to undress. And I see the largest cock I\xe2\x80\x99ve ever seen outside of virtual porn.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />I can see my HP drop as he slams into me. Not enough to worry about. My regen will take care of it shortly. It should hurt, but Master\xe2\x80\x99s figured out how to use my traits against me. I feel nothing but bliss as he pounds me, to the point where I can barely even think any more. And then, he leans forward, and whispers in my ear, <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cI AM Torgan!\xe2\x80\x9d</span> Then the debuff goes away, and my mind flew away.<br /><br /><hr /><br /><div class='spoiler'><div class='smalltext' style='margin-bottom:2px'><b>Spoiler</b> : <input type='button' value='Show' class='spoilerButton'></div><div class='spoilerContent'><div style='display: none;'><br /><div style="max-width: 100%; overflow:auto"><table><tbody><tr><td>Name</td><td>Zayn Darkmore</td><td>Alignment</td><td>Chaotic Neutral</td></tr><tr><td>Level</td><td>10</td><td>Race</td><td>Incubus</td></tr><tr><td>Class</td><td>Warlock</td><td>Sub-Class</td><td>None</td></tr><tr><td>Experience</td><td>45000/55000</td><td>Profession</td><td>Slave Trainer</td></tr><tr><td>HP</td><td>830/830</td><td>MP</td><td>1030/1230</td></tr><tr><td>HP Regen</td><td>8.3. per min</td><td>MP Regen</td><td>10.3 per min</td></tr><tr><td>Fame</td><td>1155</td><td>Infamy</td><td>420</td></tr><tr><td>0 PP</td><td>18 GP</td><td>6 SP</td><td>0 CP</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Attributes</td></tr><tr><td>STR</td><td>69(79)</td><td>INT</td><td>73(103)</td></tr><tr><td>DEX</td><td>69(79)</td><td>WIS</td><td>69(79)</td></tr><tr><td>CON</td><td>73(83)</td><td>CHA</td><td>221(231)</td></tr><tr><td>Luck</td><td>63</td><td>Attack</td><td>+30</td></tr><tr><td>Defense</td><td>+47</td><td>???</td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Points Remaining: 0</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='1'>Titles</td><td colspan='3'>The Executioner, The Sexecutioner, Corrupter, Master Chainmaker</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Resistances</td></tr><tr><td>Pierce</td><td>+15%</td><td>Bludgeoning</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Slash</td><td>+15%</td><td>Fire</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Ice</td><td></td><td>Water</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Lightning</td><td></td><td>Wind</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Earth</td><td></td><td>Light</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Dark</td><td>+30%</td><td>Charm</td><td>+10%</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>-50% Charm Resistance vs. Females (-100% if CHA equal or lower than foe)<br />+25% Stun resistance to attacks vs. crotch<br />+30% Hellfire Resistance</td></tr><tr><td>Diety</td><td colspan='3'>Sharess</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Proficiencies</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Simple Weapons<br />Exotic Weapon (Spit)<br />Swords<br />Dual Wielding<br />Bows<br />Exotic Weapon (Whips)<br />Light Armor<br />Hellfire</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Qualities</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Black Bible of Kitami Reika<br />How to Serve Woman<br />Infinite Blade Works<br />Subs or Dubs?<br />Strange Attraction<br />Sucker for a Pretty Face<br />The Usual Suspects<br />Why Would You Post Something Like That?</td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'></td></tr><tr><td colspan='4'>Ski