    <div class="portlet-body">
                        <div class="chapter-inner chapter-content">
            The journey to Fathon was not far, only a day\xe2\x80\x99s march, so we stayed the night at the Priestess\xe2\x80\x99s cabin. After a very enjoyable night (not as enjoyable for Severa, as I punished her as promised by thoroughly using her ass), and a breakfast of leftover Priestess, we set out. Incidentally, it seems that cooking skill can be used to give temporary buffs to people. The Priestess\xe2\x80\x99s meat gave us a +10% movement speed for four hours, and we ate the last of her at lunch, so we got to Fathon in the midafternoon.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />As we approached the city gates, the guards started, and then bowed to the two Princesses. <span style="color: #669933;">\xe2\x80\x9cYour Highnesses! We are so glad to see you safe! We heard what happened to your carriage. How did you escape?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Apparently, the princesses were on a diplomatic mission to human lands, when they were waylaid, the cultists used poison to overcome their escorts, and they were captured and taken to the cabin. Esyae told the guards about the Priestess, and her ritual, and how I came and stopped it. She left out some parts, like the fact that we made the Priestess into meat, but did include how I defeated that adventuring company.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />The guards turned to look at me with new eyes, and said, <span style="color: #669933;">\xe2\x80\x9cAnd who might you be?\xe2\x80\x9d</span> They didn\xe2\x80\x99t know what to make of me. High Fame led to guards being friendly, but high infamy led to them disliking you. With both relatively high, at least for low levels, I was confusing them, I think.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />I smiled, winningly. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cI am a Traveler. I first came to this world within the woods, and came upon the Priestess\xe2\x80\x99s cabin by chance. Fortunately, I was in time to stop her foul deeds. Now, my companions and I have traveled long, and could do with a hot meal and good drink.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />The head guard nodded. <span style="color: #669933;">\xe2\x80\x9cAll right, then. If you follow the main road, you\xe2\x80\x99ll find the Lady\xe2\x80\x99s Favor. Not the most expensive inn around, but they\xe2\x80\x99ve got the best food, and the owner\xe2\x80\x99s related to the local priestess of Sharess. Next to it you\xe2\x80\x99ll find the Adventurer\xe2\x80\x99s Guild. If you\xe2\x80\x99re a new Traveler as you say, you\xe2\x80\x99ll be wanting to check in there.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />The Lady\xe2\x80\x99s Favor was a typical fantasy-world type inn, though you could tell it was a fairly high end place, as it was a three story affair. There was a common room on the ground floor, which doubled as a tavern. Well the whole story is pretty clich\xc3\xa9, so I\xe2\x80\x99ll skip it. Needless to say, we got two rooms, with meals included, for three nights, paying a total of 10 Silver, 5 Copper for each room. The Princesses got one room, and my slaves and I were sharing the other. The three-night stay was so we could rest, train in classes and professions, and hopefully get transportation to the elvish kingdom, so we wouldn\xe2\x80\x99t have to walk the whole way. We probably wouldn\xe2\x80\x99t be able to afford horses for all of us, but a wagon of some sort should be within our reach, right?<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Anyways, once we had checked in to our rooms, the Princesses went to see some of the people they\xe2\x80\x99d met in the city, and my slaves followed me to the guild hall. This was actually a three-story building as well, which is impressive for a medieval city. Probably used magic to help?<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Entering the main room, we of course drew stares from people. It is common enough in games, especially with newcomers. When a newcomer has two pretty women following behind him, that tends to draw even more attention. Looking at the desk, I saw that a young man was there.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cHello there, I would like to see about registering as an adventurer.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cJust you?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAh, can slaves be registered?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cI\xe2\x80\x99m afraid not. But if the slave is a former adventurer, their ranking will help yours, and the actions of your slaves will count for completing missions. They are considered to be property, like your sword.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cVery well. I will register myself, and Severa here will need to turn in her card.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cFor the record, how did you come to have an adventurer as your slave?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cHer adventuring company, the Black Hand, was working for a Priestess conducting a dark ritual. They attacked me when I interrupted the ritual. She is the only survivor of that group.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cOh. The Black Hand was an E ranked company. Well done, for a new adventurer!\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cWell, I am a Traveler. And may I hear more about the various ranks?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cAh, well that explains it. As for the ranks, they range from F through A, and then S, SS, and SSS. Everyone undergoes tests in order to determine their ranking. Once your initial ranking has been set, you may increase your rank later through accomplishments, though you will still need to take the tests to have the rank confirmed. Used to be, there was a point system, but we found that people would cheat or outright buy their way to higher ranks, for glory or out of pride, and would wind up getting killed when they took a quest that was too advanced for them. So the current system allows for advancement, but keeps the unqualified from moving beyond their capabilities.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xc2\xa0</span><br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAnd what do these tests entail?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cA test of skills for warriors and a test of magic for mages. You can choose to do one or both tests.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAnd what other services does the guild provide?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cIn addition to verifying quest difficulty and rewards, we also will buy materials and gear you don\xe2\x80\x99t need, at a fair price based on the current market. For those who have yet to unlock their class or subclass, we have testing services that suggest paths you would be well suited to, and gives you the requirements. In addition, members of the guild may stay at the guild hall free of charge, so long as they are in good standing.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cVery well, I\xe2\x80\x99d like to complete my registration now.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cPlease fill out this form.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I filled out the form, and the clerk said that they would have it ready by the next evening. Since the test instructors had gone home for the day, we would come back the next day for my evaluation. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cBy the way, where might I seek training in various professions?\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #999933;">\xe2\x80\x9cThe Tradesman\xe2\x80\x99s Guild down by the Marketplace is where you\xe2\x80\x99ll want to go. They\xe2\x80\x99re closed for the night, but they\xe2\x80\x99ll be open early tomorrow morning. If there\xe2\x80\x99s a profession you want to learn and there isn\xe2\x80\x99t a trainer there, they\xe2\x80\x99ll at least tell you where to go.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />I thanked the clerk, who was apparently named Bill, and left, with Severa and Della in my wake. Severa had been blushing furiously this whole time, since she used to be an E rank, and was now publicly being called a slave. Oh well, she\xe2\x80\x99s going to have to get over it, since I don\xe2\x80\x99t intend on letting her go anytime soon. Neither of my slaves is getting free. A slave harem that I can take with me as we\xe2\x80\x99re fighting? Why hadn\xe2\x80\x99t I thought of this before? Oh yeah, Torgan was a light-type, and would never do such a thing. Good thing Zayn is a corrupt bastard!<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Speaking about harems and corruption, I was eager to experience more of both, so we went back to the inn for the evening meal. Nothing overly fancy, just some meat, cheese, bread, and ale, but it was all tasty stuff. You know, that kind of simple, home-style cooking that you can get together in half an hour, but satisfies much more than the little artistic plates at a five-star restaurant.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />After dinner, we went up to our room, after bidding good night to the princesses. Once the door was closed behind us, I commanded my slaves to strip, so I could examine them more closely. This was the first time we\xe2\x80\x99d been alone, after all. Of course, I also removed my clothes.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Della had blond hair reaching down to her shoulders, with blue eyes, about 5\xe2\x80\x996\xe2\x80\x9d tall. If I had to categorize her, I\xe2\x80\x99d put her down as the \xe2\x80\x98slender\xe2\x80\x99 type. Her curves weren\xe2\x80\x99t too noticeable, but they were just the right proportions, and went nicely with her B cups. She had this innocent look about her, a \xe2\x80\x98girl next door\xe2\x80\x99 type. Of course, she was also a big time S, following Loviatar. I noticed a tattoo on the small of her back, just above her butt. The girl actually had a tramp stamp with Loviatar\xe2\x80\x99s symbol!<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Severa, on the other hand, was a tall, raven-haired sex machine. Or she would be, when I was done with her. 6\xe2\x80\x99 even, she had curves to make men drool and women weep, which were only accentuated when she wore those leather pants she favored. Her hourglass figure was only enhanced by some nice Ds up top. Unlike Della, who had neatly trimmed her hair between her legs, Severa was shaved. Apparently, she was used to being the dominant one in a relationship, and being forced to be my plaything was an adjustment to her. Her hair was normally pulled back into a pony-tail, but was now loose, reaching down to her waist.<br />\xc2\xa0<br />Looking over my beauties, I circled, pinching and prodding them as I talked, making sure to tease them as a bit of foreplay. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAs you heard, I\xe2\x80\x99m going to be an adventurer, and you two will be coming with me when I go into the field. We still have to get classes for myself and Della, and you two need professions.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cc6633;">\xe2\x80\x9cI thought \xe2\x80\x98sex slave\xe2\x80\x99 was going to be our profession now.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> Ah, Severa, thank you for that interruption.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cSevera, bend over and grab your ankles. Della, spank Severa\xe2\x80\x99s bottom while I\xe2\x80\x99m speaking.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> I think I\xe2\x80\x99m going to train Severa into an M, and Della into a \xe2\x80\x98switch\xe2\x80\x99. That\xe2\x80\x99ll work best, yeah. As the first smacks of Della\xe2\x80\x99s hand against Severa\xe2\x80\x99s rear echo through the room along with Severa\xe2\x80\x99s whimpers, I continue. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cYou\xe2\x80\x99ll both be having plenty of sex, don\xe2\x80\x99t worry. I\xe2\x80\x99m an incubus after all, and so I have needs. But I want my property to be productive, as well. While I could whore you out, I thought it would be better for you both to learn something useful. So we\xe2\x80\x99ll be going down to the marketplace tomorrow and see what professions are available. And, depending on price, we might even visit the slave market and find another to join our group.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #cc66ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAnother, Master?\xe2\x80\x9d</span> Della spoke up, even as she continued spanking her fellow slave. Her cheeks were flushed, so I could tell she was getting excited by the situation.<br />\xc2\xa0<br /><span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cOh yes, I intend to have a full party eventually. You and Severa will be good for healing and for stealth attacks and other such things. But we could use a true mage or a warrior that specializes in defense. That will allow us to face a wider array of enemies, and provide better safety for you all. As a Traveler, if I die, I will return after a time, but that is not true for those of you born in this world.\xe2\x80\x9d</span><br />\xc2\xa0<br />Della nodded, signaling that she understood, and I smiled. <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cNow, Della, step away from Severa. As a reward, you may touch yourself as you watch.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> And with that, I stepped in behind Severa, and spat on my hands using the saliva to lubricate my shaft <span style="color: #3366ff;">\xe2\x80\x9cAnd Severa, it seems you need a lesson in what happens to slaves who mouth off.\xe2\x80\x9d</span> And I shoved myself all the way inside her reddened ass.
        </div>
